description:
Minecraft Server. We start things off today by finishing up the second level of Hurtin Hermits. Then we meet up with Bdubs in our new office to guide him through his Shade-E-E's training. The Ender Chest storage room gets it's finishing touches and Docm accepts a nasty deal.
